  2409 				;  Per-voice level meters: 4 horizontal VU bars at scan 9-13, bar width =
  2410 				;  voice envelope level * 3 px. Drawn INCREMENTALLY -- each frame only the
  2411 				;  delta between the old and new level is set/cleared, so meters animating
  2412 				;  with the envelopes cost a few pixels per voice, not a full redraw.
  2413 				; ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
