  3198 				;        0 WAVE  1 VOL  2 OCT  3 ATK  4 DEC | 5 SUS  6 REL  7 CLK  8 LFOR 9 LFOD
  3199 				;        left column (0-4)                  | right column (5-9)
  3200 				; INDEX ORDER == VISUAL ORDER so UP/DOWN steps through the panel as drawn:
  3201 				;   left column top->bottom (0-5), then right column top->bottom (6-10).
  3202 				;        0 WAVE 1 VOL 2 OCT 3 ATK 4 DEC 5 DET | 6 SUS 7 REL 8 CLK 9 LFOR 10 LFOD
  3203 				;  left column 0-5             | right column 6-11 (incl ARP=11)
